reviewText: This French movie was delivered on time.  However, you can't play it on a U.S. VCR (missing some code).  I can play it on my small screen computer and find it has no subtitle.  Bottom line: a great disappointment.
For people who loves COMEDEY, this is a big chance to laugh. Louis de  Funes is one of the best comedeans I ever saw, he is full of humor. It is a  must see.
